{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"dd5291b472","title":"在河南省文联文学座谈会上的发言","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"ab2657d42f","index":0,"year":1955,"month":6,"day":1,"articleId":"dd5291b472"}],"tags":[{"id":"e23dcf99fa","name":"发言","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"59a24082d1","name":"李索开"},{"id":"9ec5840208","name":"河南"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"d57e82e84f","type":"title","text":"在河南省文联文学座谈会上的发言","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"dd5291b472"},{"id":"dffc45628e","type":"authors","text":"河南李索开","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"dd5291b472"},{"id":"81ff6593f4","type":"subtitle","text":"(李索开：诗人，《奔流》编辑)","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"dd5291b472"},{"id":"d87a7e15ce","type":"paragraph","text":"河南人民出版社，大官容易小官难缠，《奔流》广告到一号还不给登，说怕越登订户越多。出书质量低，作者不愿拿稿子去，愿到外地出书。","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"dd5291b472"},{"id":"735ac2a513","type":"paragraph","text":"编辑也有苦恼，无社会地位，无政治地位。人代会编辑就没有参加的，作者写文章能参加。现在是一级级的，开鲁迅纪念会、作者在主席台是主席团，编辑只能当记录。","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"dd5291b472"},{"id":"7423a1f26d","type":"paragraph","text":"编者、作者、读者有矛盾，质量低，读者有意见，不发表作者有意见，编辑两头受挤，这也是苦恼。","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"dd5291b472"},{"id":"9aa5c786a1","type":"paragraph","text":" （根据记录整理）","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"dd5291b472"},{"id":"f4b00f16e6","type":"paragraph","text":" 来源：《苏金伞右派集团言论与作品》（河南省文学美术工作者联合会，1958年）。","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"dd5291b472"}],"page":{"id":"cc425b1408","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"dd5291b472","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}